[STEP 4] If we exclude `nums[i-1]`, then `dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j]`. If we include `nums[i-1]`, then `dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j - nums[i-1]] + 1`. We choose the maximum of these two possibilities: `dp[i][j] = max(dp[i-1][j], dp[i-1][j - nums[i-1]] + 1)`.

